INSERT INTO anime(name,description,studio,publisher,image) VALUES ("Minori Scramble!","Tamaki is an elementary school girl. Her father Dr. Yagiyama loves penguins and his excessive lectures about penguins makes Tamaki hate them. In order to get rid of her hatred of penguins, he engineers the penguin-roid \'Minori\'. Tamaki and Minori run about the neighborhood to solve troubles caused by her father.","43/ufotable, ufotable","","https://myanimelist.cdn-dena.com/images/anime/6/31903.jpg");
INSERT INTO anime(name,description,studio,publisher,image) VALUES ("Junod","Mii and Yuko, two junior high school students are visiting Hiroshima Peace Memorial Park on a school trip when they come upon a monument dedicated to Dr. Marcel Junod standing forlornly in a corner of the park. They wonder who Dr. Junod was and what he did. Just then they are bathed in a strange light and transported back to Europe, more than 70 years before. It is 1935. The young Dr. Junod, who has been working in a hospital in Mulhouse, France, is heading to Ethiopia as a delegate of the ICRC. Time travelers Mii and Yuko set off along Dr. Junod's path of hardship and turmoil. In Ethiopia, Dr. Junod witnesses attacks on Red Cross workers and the use of poison gas. One after another people are felled. The young doctor sees firsthand the horrors of war, but buoyed by an indomitable spirit he willingly offers a helping hand to those who are suffering as a result of the war. Dr. Junod's work takes him from Ethiopia to Spain and across the European battlefields of World War II. He works to improve the treatment of prisoners of war and arranges prisoner exchanges. He establishes a method for prisoners and their families to write to each other. He secures routes for the delivery of relief supplies. As a humanitarian, Dr. Junod offers moral support to the weak. Seeing that, Mii and Yuko reflect on their own lives and problems. (Source: official website)","101/Studio_Hibari, Studio Hibari","","https://myanimelist.cdn-dena.com/images/anime/9/26355.jpg");
INSERT INTO anime(name,description,studio,publisher,image) VALUES ("Wolf Guy","Akira lnugami is infected with a terrible poison. The only known antidote has an unfortunate side effect-it turns him into a werewolf. He opts for survival but then has to cope with his new desires and with the attention of the military, which is in terested in using his affliction for its own purposes. (Source: The Anime Encyclopedia)","7/JCStaff, J.C.Staff","","https://myanimelist.cdn-dena.com/images/anime/12/72486.jpg");
INSERT INTO anime(name,description,studio,publisher,image) VALUES ("Transformers Superlink Special","Episode 43.5, \'Distribution\', is a comedic special show which commemorates 500 episodes of Transformers in Japan (however, since that total includes assorted Japanese series, the west is still some distance away from this number). When aired in Japan, it did not air in the usual timeslot for Superlink, and is not in any sort of chronological order - It features the Autobots playing a video game training simulator, which they certainly do not have time to do between episodes 42 and 44. (Source: Wikipedia)","60/Actas, Actas","","https://myanimelist.cdn-dena.com/images/anime/5/26361.jpg");
